title: Frame
body: Hy, i ve got a quick question. i ve been gold 4 last season and now i should have got a golden frame and the skin of maokai but i ve got none. Any reasons? Thanks

replies.body: We can help with this individually through a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new).  Reach out to us and we'll offer more context.  We'll reply back asap!
